Reasoning: The paper deals with the statistical characterization of the sum of random variables in the context of wireless communication systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the performance evaluation of wireless communication applications, which suggests that it could belong to cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.ST (Statistics). The use of moment matching method and asymptotic expressions indicates that it could also belong to cs.MS (Mathematical Software) or cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
